<p><%= @emails.length > 1 ? "Hi all," : "Hi there," %></p>

<p>
  Congrats! Your donation goal of <%= render_money @goal.amount_cents %> has been reached after <%= distance_of_time_in_words @goal.tracking_since, DateTime.now %>!
  <% if Flipper.enabled?(:organization_announcements_tier_1_2025_07_07, @event) %>
    If you wish, <%= link_to "create an announcement", event_announcements_new_url(@event.slug, template: :donation_goal_reached) %> to let your followers know that you've reached your goal.
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>Here are all the donations that helped to contribute to this goal:</p>
<ul>
<% @donations.each do |donation| %>
  <li>
    <%= donation.name(show_anonymous: true) %> <%= "anonymously" if donation.anonymous %> donated <%= render_money donation.amount %>
  </li>
<% end %>
</ul>

<p>You can adjust your donation goal on the <%= link_to "organization settings page", edit_event_url(@event) %>.</p>

<p>
  From,<br>
  The HCB Team
</p>
